   Daxue Market Research
   consumer panel China

   CONSUMER PANEL

   Our panel of consumers gathers various samples of Chinese consumers
   (age, sex, income, geographical areas, consuming patterns, etc) which
   allow you to better understand the evolution of the market, the
   awareness toward your brand and any driver of growth in your industry.
   View Details
   Market research China

   MARKET ANALYSIS

   Daxue Consulting serves its clients with data-driven analysis of their
   market. We use a full range of close-to-market and tailored
   methodologies to collect the most reliable and relevant data that
   satisfies your needs of information and your ambitions in the Chinese
   market.
   View Details
   focus group China

   FOCUS GROUPS

   Daxue Consulting collect qualitative data to provide you with the
   deepest understanding of Chinese consumer perceptions, buying criteria
   and product preferences. Our team will setup every step of your focus
   groups in China, including recruitment, moderation and further
   analysis.
   View Details
   Omnibus survey China

   SENSORY RESEARCH

   Daxue Consulting offers the design, set up and execution for any
   sensory research in China. It includes discrimination tests (overall
   difference and attribute-specific), as well as descriptive test and
   home-usability testing (HUT).
   View Details

   Daxue Tech
   Eye tracking China

   EYE-TRACKING

   Eye tracking is the measurement of eye activity. Daxue Consulting uses
   this research method to collect data and to analyze the visual path of
   Chinese consumers across an interface such as a website, a mobile APP,
   a packaging or even printed ads.
   View Details
   consumer panel China

   STORE-CHECKS

   Daxue Consulting favors agile and close-to-market data-collection
   methodologies in China. In-store data is one of the best sources of
   information to better understand your market and your competition frame
   in China. We have developed our in-house mobile APP The Store-Checkers.
   View Details
   online survey China

   USER-EXPERIENCE RESEARCH (UX)

   Daxue Consulting support you to better fit the needs of your end-users
   in China. Our team uses various research methods to collect data and to
   analyze the usage path of Chinese consumers across digital interfaces
   such as websites or mobile APP.
   View Details

   Daxue Management Consulting
   Market entry China

   MARKET ENTRY

   Regarding your ambition in the Chinese market, our team provides you
   with the essential data-driven knowledge to setup your strategic
   go-to-market plan in China. Our project managers work with your team to
   fully adapt your offer and marketing plan to the Chinese market.
   View Details
   Marketing activation China

   MARKETING ACTIVATION

   Daxue Consulting's solution to marketing activation in China aims at
   setting up a pragmatic and segmented plan to significantly improve your
   market shares toward targeted and quantified segments of Chinese
   consumers.
   View Details
   Monitoring plan China

   BRANDING STRATEGY

   Daxue Consulting provides branding plan in China that are data-driven,
   supported by the experience and knowledge of the Chinese market. It
   includes brand naming, promotion road-map and marketing value
   proposition validation with Chinese consumers.
   View Details

   Daxue Strategy
   Market strategy China

   MARKET SIZING

   Daxue Consulting offers market sizing in China. Our team triangulate
   bottom-up, top-down and distribution analysis approach to provide the
   most accurate and reliable evaluation of your market potential in
   China.
   View Details
   Business Intelligence China

   BUSINESS INTELLIGENCE

   Daxue Consulting offers to its clients solutions to collect and
   aggregate data that gravitates around the company’s environment (stock
   market data, category pricing audit, social listening, etc.)
   View Details
   Business turnover China

   INNOVATION MANAGEMENT

   Daxue Consulting has developed specific research and operational
   implementation method to favor open innovation in China. It includes
   tech scouting, agile strategic plan, business turnaround.
   View Details

