   OUR STRENGTHS
     *
     * Market Research China Firm’s Strengths
       Our extensive experience in Chinese markets, university connections
       and unique data-gathering network separate Daxue from other
       consulting firms in China. Our obsession with quality data in
       China’s dynamic and confusing environment means your business
       decisions will be based on an informed and realistic understanding
       of your market.

     *
     * Daxue Consulting offers agile stragy consulting in China. We
       leverage the best resources and tech-driven data collection in
       order to provide our clients a wide range of business Intelligence
       tools to help their strategic decisions, innovation management and
       plan for a successful development in China. Our role is to help
       business units to achieve leadership positions.

   Our services and methodologies for market research in China

   Our methodologies use quantitative and qualitative information to
   analyze and understand the Chinese market. Our services include
   different market intelligence tools such as:
     * Market research
     * Focus groups
     * Mystery shopping
     * Store checks
     * Market study
     * Online survey
     * Market report
     * Market analysis in China
     * Marketing research in China
     * Strategy in China
     * Retail & distribution consulting
     * In-depth and quantitative interviews
     * Business plan
     * China entry strategy
     * Open innovation management
     * Pricing strategy research
     * User experience research
     * Sensory research

   The expertise of Daxue Consulting

   Since 2009, Daxue Consulting has served Multinationals (MNC) and SME in
   numerous sectors such as FMCG sectors, food and beverage, technologies,
   real estate projects, travel, leisure, E-commerce websites, luxury
   fields, smart city, and fashion as well as industrial and BtoB
   businesses. The projects and market surveys managed by our consulting
   firm are based on well-known and fully mastered methodologies. On top
   of the projects managed by our firm, specialized senior consultants in
   retail, luxury, China, automotive, design, and E-commerce are called
   upon in order to give perspective and moderate workshops or focus
   groups. We provided market research in Shanghai, Beijing, Guangzhou,
   Shenzheng and all over China. You can find our website in Hong-Kong and
   China.

   One client, one unique experience

   Our work is focused on our clients and we adapt our methodologies to
   their questions to get the best information possible to solve their
   challenges in China. We consider each market research project as a
   unique, innovative and new challenge. Over the years, a multitude of
   differing projects have helped develop our technical tools in
   leveraging social networks, forums and new technologies for our market
   survey in China. These tools make it possible to approach the Chinese
   markets and to provide consulting in a unique, effective and
   competitive way. We are able to examine our clients’ technological
   deficiencies and suggest methods to improve their operations in China.
   Following this examination, we can develop and program new useful tools
   and suitable methodologies to improve our clients businesses. No
   business today can deny the need for technology in their daily business
   operations and our consulting team wants to provide you the best tools
   to improve these operations in China.

   Efficiency throughout China for China Market Research

   Daxue Market Research Group has offices in Beijing, Shanghai and
   Hong-Kong. Moreover, we are able to manage market surveys all over
   China through our network of project assistants and panels. Through our
   contacts and university networks, we are able to leverage this resource
   to make it a proxy to understand the entire market. Our target audience
   is actually connected with all of the segments we are interested in and
   we particularly aim to work with MBAs to serve as samples to better
   understand the thoughts and consumptions patterns of the emerging
   middle and affluent classes in China. Leveraging this proxy makes it
   possible for us to conduct business in various fields such as
   agri-business, utilities, retail, fashion, FMCG, food & beverage and
   many other fields.

   Information, the key to success in China

   Useful market research requires thorough, honest and candid approaches
   to make sure we interview the right sample and ask the right questions
   to obtain accurate information. Understanding competition, pricing of
   products and services, consumer paths, consumer values, design, price
   and product acceptance, locations of shops and products in retail,
   creation of marketing planning, choice of marketing channels and
   business plans are necessary to gather useful and successful marketing
   research in China. As one of the most competitive companies for China
   market research, we offer our expertise to our clients who want to
   understand the very unique and specific Chinese market landscape.

