Who We Are

   Daxue Consulting is a China-based market research and strategy agency.
   Created on the campus of Beijing Daxue in 2009, Daxue Consulting has
   strong roots on Chinese market but also an international vision and
   team. Daxue Consulting now has offices in Beijing and Shanghai and its
   team is composed of local and overseas-educated Chinese and
   China-educated foreign project managers.

