   服务内容
     *
     * World class quality
       Your project is managed from proposal to presentation by
       professional project leaders with years of market research
       experience in China from top corporations and universities. They
       provide careful thought to the approach and the selection of
       effective, well-known and proven methodologies to fit your needs
       while meeting every deadline. Our knowledge of research and of
       China ensures conclusions you can trust. We help you to identify
       the impact of new trends.

     *
     * Nationwide Reach
       Our unique network and our strong China-based roots allow us to
       collect large-scale data. Through our data-base of China-based
       market insiders and professionals, our market surveys in China can
       reach any industry.

     *
     * Responsiveness & Flexibility
       Support from your project manager is just a phone call away.
       Clients tell us how pleased they are to find their senior
       consultant had researched their business and understood their
       unique challenges in China.

     *
     * Tech-driven approach
       All our strategy consulting services are 100% data-driven. To
       perform data collection, we develop innovative and tech-driven
       methodologies managed by experienced full-time in-house
       professionals. Our experience and knowledge of Chinese market
       dynamics allow us to design tailored, agile and pragmatic research
       designs and to always use the relevant tools according to the
       client's situation

     *
     * Perfect partner in China
       While Daxue Consulting mainly serves International brands or firms,
       some of our clients are consulting and market research firms which
       partner with us to cover their projects in China. As we are
       focusing on China’s market, we will never compete with our partners
       abroad and as such we are the best, safest and most reliable
       partner they can find in China.

     *
     * Our clients
       Our clients are both multinational corporations and medium-sized
       companies from basically anywhere in the World. With hundreds of
       projects each year, our management team developed a deep
       understanding of each sector and companies' situation needs and
       stake on the Chinese market.

   客户的体验是最好的推荐
   logos

   OUR STRENGTHS
     *
     * Market Research China Firm’s Strengths
       Our extensive experience in Chinese markets, university connections
       and unique data-gathering network separate Daxue from other
       consulting firms in China. Our obsession with quality data in
       China’s dynamic and confusing environment means your business
       decisions will be based on an informed and realistic understanding
       of your market.

     *
     * Daxue Consulting offers consulting in China. We leverage the best
       resources in order to provide our clients a wide range of business
       Intelligence tools to help their strategic decisions and plan for a
       successful development in China. Our role is to help business units
       to achieve leadership positions.

   Our services and methodologies for market research in China

   Our methodologies use quantitative and qualitative information to
   analyze and understand the Chinese market. Our services include
   different market intelligence tools such as:
     * Market research
     * Focus groups
     * Mystery shopping
     * Store checks
     * Market study
     * Online survey
     * Market report
     * Market analysis in China
     * Marketing research in China
     * Strategy in China
     * Retail & distribution consulting
     * In-depth and quantitative interviews
     * Business plan
     * China entry strategy

   The expertise of Daxue Consulting

   Since 2009, Daxue Consulting has served Multinationals (MNC) and SME in
   numerous sectors such as FMCG sectors, food and beverage, technologies,
   real estate projects, travel, leisure, E-commerce websites, luxury
   fields, and fashion as well as industrial and BtoB businesses. The
   projects and market surveys managed by our consulting firm are based on
   well-known and fully mastered methodologies. On top of the projects
   managed by our firm, specialized senior consultants in retail, luxury,
   China, automotive, design, and E-commerce are called upon in order to
   give perspective and moderate workshops or focus groups. We provided
   market research in Shanghai, Beijing, Guangzhou, Shenzheng and all over
   China. You can find our website in Hong-Kong and China.

   One client, one unique experience

   Our work is focused on our clients and we adapt our methodologies to
   their questions to get the best information possible to solve their
   challenges in China. We consider each market research project as a
   unique and new challenge. Over the years, a multitude of differing
   projects have helped develop our technical tools in leveraging social
   networks, forums and new technologies for our market survey in China.
   These tools make it possible to approach the Chinese markets and to
   provide consulting in a unique, effective and competitive way. We are
   able to examine our clients’ technological deficiencies and suggest
   methods to improve their operations in China. Following this
   examination, we can develop and program new useful tools and suitable
   methodologies to improve our clients businesses. No business today can
   deny the need for technology in their daily business operations and our
   consulting team wants to provide you the best tools to improve these
   operations in China.

   Efficiency throughout China for China Market Research

   Daxue Market Research Group has offices in Beijing, Shanghai and
   Hong-Kong. Moreover, we are able to manage market surveys all over
   China through our network of project assistants and panels. Through our
   contacts and university networks, we are able to leverage this resource
   to make it a proxy to understand the entire market. Our target audience
   is actually connected with all of the segments we are interested in and
   we particularly aim to work with MBAs to serve as samples to better
   understand the thoughts and consumptions patterns of the emerging
   middle and affluent classes in China. Leveraging this proxy makes it
   possible for us to conduct business in various fields such as
   agri-business, utilities, retail, fashion, FMCG, food & beverage and
   many other fields.

   Information, the key to success in China

   Useful market research requires thorough, honest and candid approaches
   to make sure we interview the right sample and ask the right questions
   to obtain accurate information. Understanding competition, pricing of
   products and services, consumer paths, consumer values, design, price
   and product acceptance, locations of shops and products in retail,
   creation of marketing planning, choice of marketing channels and
   business plans are necessary to gather useful and successful marketing
   research in China. As one of the most competitive companies for China
   market research, we offer our expertise to our clients who want to
   understand the very unique and specific Chinese market landscape.

