Who We Are

   Daxue Consulting is a China-based market research and strategy agency.
   Created on the campus of Beijing Daxue in 2009, Daxue Consulting has
   strong roots on Chinese market but also an international vision and
   team. Daxue Consulting now has offices in Beijing and Shanghai and its
   team is composed of local and overseas-educated Chinese and
   China-educated foreign project managers.

In The Press

     * Daxue Talks 2: Everything you need to know about WFOE in China in
       2019
     * Daxue Talks transcript #2: 5 minutes talk with a business lawyer
       about WFOE in China in 2019
     * Chinese insurance market: Mainland Chinese buy insurance products
       in Hong Kong and make asset allocation | Daxue Consulting
     * China negative list: Is your company qualified to run a business in
       China? | Daxue Consulting
     * Huawei issue: What are the reactions of Chinese netizens to the
       sanction to Huawei from the U.S.? | Daxue Consulting
     * Chinese companies listed in Hong Kong: Why is HK so attractive? |
       Daxue Consulting
     * The counterfeit good industry in modern China | Daxue Consulting
     * Leveraging Guanxi for Business – Approaching the mindset behind
       Guanxi | Daxue Consulting
     * 5G Networks are ready for worldwide commercialization, powered by
       Chinese Technology | Daxue Consulting
     * Anti-Pollution Mask Industry in China: An Enforced Trend | Daxue
       Consulting
     * The Red Packets advent in anticipation of the upcoming 2019 Spring
       Festival | Daxue Consulting
     * How eye-tracking is used to understand Chinese consumers | Daxue
       Consulting

   daxue consulting is owned by Ever Access trading Limited

   Ever access trading owns 博圣轩投资顾问有限公司上海分公司

